\cs44\insrsid15095451\charrsid2645883  money to pay for the journey and for food.' And I said to him, `To tell }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid10502878\charrsid2645883 thee the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs44\insrsid15095451\charrsid2645883  truth, I have no money, neither have I food. But 
I shall go with them and shall go aboard. And they shall feed me, whether they want to or not. I have a body -- they shall take it instead of pay for the journey.' I was suddenly filled with a desire to go, Abba, to have more lovers who could satisfy my p
assion. I told }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid10502878\charrsid2645883 thee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid15095451\charrsid2645883 , Abba Zosimas, not to force me to tell }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 
