hem were waiting for more travelers whilst others had gone ashore). Shamelessly, as usual, I mixed with the crowd, saying, `Take me with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid10502878\charrsid2645883 thee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 
