\par How shall I relate to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid10502878\charrsid2645883 thee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs44\insrsid15095451\charrsid2645883  what happened after this? Whose tongue can tell, whose ears can take in all 
